        "## What Students Should Notice {.unnumbered}\n",
        "\n",
        "- Cleaning choices strongly affect which terms dominate.\n",
        "- TF-IDF emphasizes distinctive terms instead of just frequent ones.\n",
        "- This small-scale workflow is the same pattern students will use in `M01_A`, just with a much larger SEC corpus.\n",
